<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="setbuf" id="setbuf">setbuf</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstdio&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">void</span> <span class="kw3">setbuf</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">FILE</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>stream, <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>buffer <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Sets the internal buffer to use for stream operations. It should be at least <code>BUFSIZ</code> characters long.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "setbuf" [1-217] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>stream</code> - file stream to set the internal buffer to.
</p>

<p>
<code>buffer</code> - buffer for the stream to use. If it is <code>NULL</code>, the buffering is turned off.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Parameters" [218-386] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

none
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "Return value" [387-414] -->
